The most important issues:
--------------------------

- ddftpd deletes upload if the filename is longer than 31 characters.

- better FidoNet support

- enhancements to ddftpd (virtual file system, easier downloading)

- better configuration utility

- better documentation 

- get rid of yacc/bison requirement during build

